Package: docxreview
Title: Extract Review Feedback from Word Documents
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Paul", "Schmidt", , "paul.schmidt@biomath.de",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Extract comments and tracked changes from reviewed Word
    documents (.docx) and return them as structured data or formatted
    Markdown. Designed for workflows where documents are rendered from
    Quarto or R Markdown, reviewed in Microsoft Word, and feedback needs
    to be processed programmatically â€” particularly with Claude Code
    and btw for AI-assisted review processing.
